kpi_info.title: UNSUCCESSFUL INTER RNC HHO CAUSED BY HSPA SCC
kpi_info.use: The number of failed inter-RNC hard handovers triggered by HSPA serving cell change. This counter is updated only for the HSPA serving cell before the HHO operation. UPDATED:When the CN responds with RANAP: RELOCATION PREPARATION FAILURE or the UE responds with RRC: TRANSPORT CHANNEL RECONFIGURATION FAILURE.
